### Create `.gitignore` file
Create a file named `.gitignore` in your project root with this content:
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.env
venv/
.venv/

# Model files (too large for GitHub)
*.pkl
*.h5

# Database files
db/*.json
db/*.csv

# Large datasets
*.csv

# Streamlit
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
